# NOTE: Terraform does not allow a backend "local" block to override a cloud {}
# block — they are incompatible block types. This file cannot be used to bypass
# Terraform Cloud for local applies.
#
# To run terraform plan/apply locally, set TF_TOKEN_app_terraform_io to a valid
# Terraform Cloud API token and run terraform init + plan/apply normally.
#
# For syntax validation only (no state), use:
#   terraform init -backend=false
#   terraform validate
